name: 3D Elite Sniper Shooter
description:
Customize excellent guns and shooting effects with freedom.

View guns in a 3D environment, view them from different angles, choose one of them and enjoy the effects and sounds of the shot. Hold this great gun in your hand and you will feel what it looks like in real life.u are careful, you can find small but pretty effective methods and pitfalls to kill them all.Enjoy Elite Sniper Shooter committed to the action!
